title: Death Sworn Skins??
body: I was extremely excited to buy the death sworn skins but they are not available to buy in the store or skin selections. Whats up with that?

replies.body: Skins don't typically hit the store on the same day as the patch. Make sure to check the shop for those skins a little later on!

replies.poster: K XD A XD T XD A
replies.body: Rito said it would come out today, just the question, when exactly, i really want that kat skin
